{
  "stem": "20581.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The most valuable or the most heroic person for the-- what he did for the Jewish Berihah.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was the one who, he used to give us [NON-ENGLISH] documents, so we could-- [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "About Captain Novinsky, I gotta tell you this story.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "One time, we were sending people-- also, we were sending people to all different zones.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Germany and Austria were divided between three governments, or three people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was between the American zone, was the British zone, and it was the Russian.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So what we used to do, the first thing, was the main job was to bring the people out from the Russian zone.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "To bring them from the Russian zone, we used to bring them to the American zone.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "OK?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One time, also, in there, [INAUDIBLE] we were-- I was bringing people over from Vienna, to the American zone.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "To [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was the border in there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Linz, near-- we had a camp in Linz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And for some reasons, the, the Americans didn't want to let any people in there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They didn't want to let in any Jews from the Russian zone to the American.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was in the train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, and they came on the train.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were asking, who is the leader?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Who brings you in here?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One stupid girl said-- points on me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She say, he's the one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So, they took me off the train.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the soldier was about 6 foot tall.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he says to me, why do you do this?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, what am I doing?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't do nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He say, they told me that you're the leader.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I say, I'm a nobody.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I says, I'm the same one, like, like any other one.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He say, no, that's not true.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
